    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于这款游戏</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>&quot;球游侠&quot;是一款角色会自动进行攻击操作,而玩家对角色拖动以进行移动操作的游戏,并随着游戏的通关,玩家会遇见不同的怪物,并可以从冒险中获得不同的道具和武器,在升级的同时以自己的喜好方向去强化,在不断的关卡挑战之下前进吧!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746280/extras/a6cbdebccf65c7cd8f11a6312dae43e3.poster.avif?t=1633612056\" width=720 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746280/extras/a6cbdebccf65c7cd8f11a6312dae43e3.webm?t=1633612056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746280/extras/a6cbdebccf65c7cd8f11a6312dae43e3.mp4?t=1633612056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>操作方法:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>只需要鼠标操作</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在大地图上时</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>两次点击闪烁点进入场景</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在场景时</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>拖动角色进行移动</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>将角色拖动至场景边缘进入另外的房间</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746280/extras/448bc201f52bfa05eab6911fef93b655.poster.avif?t=1633612056\" width=720 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746280/extras/448bc201f52bfa05eab6911fef93b655.webm?t=1633612056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746280/extras/448bc201f52bfa05eab6911fef93b655.mp4?t=1633612056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>点击右下角BAG打开背包<br></li><li>拖动背包物品进行各种操作</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你可以在冒险中寻找各种道具,挑战各种怪物,并作出你喜欢的搭配。<br></li><li>游侠的走向由玩家自己决定,想成为法师?可以!,想成为战士?也可以!<br></li><li>当然,你也可以一手拿剑,一手拿杖,只要你喜欢。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >各式各样的道具与武器</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>玩家可以在冒险中获取效果不同的武器,商店也会在你推进冒险时持续会进货新的武器,武器不一定会越后面越强,强度主要取决于玩家的等级。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >各式各样的怪物</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>每一关卡都有不同的怪物,不同的怪物有不同的攻击机制,和外表。<br></li><li>当然,也有掉落物,掉落物包括杂项,道具和武器等。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >钓鱼</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>我相信喜欢玩JRPG的人都喜欢钓鱼,所以也加入了钓鱼系统,这个在冒险途中就会遇到,相当于一个小零食吧</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746280/extras/54b0ba5854cdae12c7a835fef510ba73.poster.avif?t=1633612056\" width=720 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746280/extras/54b0ba5854cdae12c7a835fef510ba73.webm?t=1633612056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746280/extras/54b0ba5854cdae12c7a835fef510ba73.mp4?t=1633612056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>有什么游戏问题或者意见可以联系作者",
